### SlimeVR Safety information translations

title = EN: Instructions for safe use

warning_list = To prevent damage or malfunction and ensure correct use of the product, please observe the following:
warning_list-water = Do not expose the product to water or moisture.
warning_list-heat = Do not expose the product to heat.
warning_list-aux = The AUX port is only intended to be connected to official auxiliary trackers. Improper use may cause the product to malfunction. 
warning_list-hotplug = Do not plug or unplug extensions while the product is powered on.
warning_list-strap = Do not overtighten straps. This can reduce circulation and lead to injury.

warning_rf = This product generates RF radiation. This could cause interference with cardiac pacemakers, implanted defibrillators (ICDs), and other implants. Maintain at least 15cm / 6" separation between the implanted device and the product, and follow the implant safety instructions.

warning_battery = The product contains a lithium battery. Improper handling of a lithium battery can cause damage or malfunction, which in extreme cases can pose a risk of: heat generation, fire development, smoke or gas development, and explosion. 

warning_battery-unattended = Do not leave the product unattended during charging.
warning_battery-psu = Only charge the product using an external power supply rated for 5V DC.
